l automatically be configured to       trigger again every repeat seconds later, until stopped manually.      </p>     </dd>        </dl>   </div>   <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-evtimer.set-returnvalues">   <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>   <p class="para">    没有返回值。   </p>  </div>  <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/class.evtimer.php">EvTimer</a></div></div>
